    "Firstly, the use of LLM means that the system quality consistency cannot be guaranteed with model updates.",
    "While commercial LLMs were used in this experiment for accuracy enhancement, using open-source LLMs can improve transparency.",
    "Additionally, the system cannot determine service specifications across multiple needs.",
